糕即完成。 蛋糕出爐先冷卻後,再放入冰箱冷藏1個小時以上。用刀子沿著模型輕輕劃一圈,取下蛋糕即完成。"},{"pid":"b147239964ea155a16d3f41f48acce65a2dc1951","tid":427323,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"有事鐘出無艷<br />\n無事夏迎春核"},{"pid":"ef7a2b9901793cd08137948347154881e3969d01","tid":427323,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"044bda6891307e12e16f68d1d13732abd69f200e","tid":427323,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>夏迎春呀咁都唔識<br />\n<br />\n恥笑開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傻閪樓主</blockquote><br />\n真心膠都分唔到 放工出下post 大家開心咪幾好 <br />\n<br />\n下下提老母"},{"pid":"323e21a6b4733d9ed97aabb450e74234dc0fb09c","tid":427323,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呀你咁醒嘅</blockquote><br />\n係呀"},{"pid":"fd2660b3a8c5855f2c84a58d1f149949db8108db","tid":427323,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>夏迎春呀咁都唔識<br />\n<br />\n恥笑開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 傻閪樓主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你現在聚腳於創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/